<scriptment id="20000" point="naka_quit" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-06-15" status="final" >
	<part>
	    <narration>While doing whatever she does after work, Yuki looks over her shoulder. She somehow spots a man on a mountain.<comment>Extremely fast (about eight seconds long) dolly zoom to the mountainside (if the technology allows; otherwise, just dolly).</comment>The man pushes a Ferrari full of Sega memorabilia off the side of a mountain. It's not Suzuki.</narration>
	    <line id="1000" voicelang="ja" speaker="yuki">What a strange thing to do in the middle of nowhere.</line>
	    <comment>Japanese translators: look to the word "middle."</comment>
	</part>
</scriptment>
	    
            